'''Lotter''' was a [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] who was responsible for enslaving the people of [[Vald]] before ordering their extermination shortly after the defeat of the Empire by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. The New Republic did not take word of Lotter's genocide lightly and so sent a group of individuals to track Lotter down, though Lotter had long since fled, leaving behind only whispered rumors.<ref name="Basic Training">''{{InQuestCite|33|Basic Training|nolink=1}}''</ref>

